The result of the move request was: '''not moved.''' The opposes have it by quality and quantity of argument. Recent events don’t necessarily change this article’s topic, given the multiple decades it covers before the June conflict. <small>([[Wikipedia:Requested moves/Closing instructions#Closure by a page mover|closed by non-admin page mover]])</small> [[User:Garsh2|Garsh]] ([[User talk:Garsh2|talk]]) 04:17, 23 June 2025 (UTC)
