*'''Oppose''' The page people are looking for is [[2024 Iran–Israel conflict]], but we should do more to promote it. This covers a lengthy cold war, not the current war. [[User:PickleG13|PickleG13]] ([[User talk:PickleG13|talk]]) 23:19, 17 June 2025 (UTC)

*'''Oppose''' - As per [[User:TGCP|TGCP]] and [[User:KiltedKangaroo|KiltedKangaroo]]. [[User:Thegreatrebellion|Thegreatrebellion]] ([[User talk:Thegreatrebellion|talk]]) 10:01, 19 June 2025 (UTC)

